 A yearly subscription is refundable within 14 days of purchase and includes a 365-day membership. As required by South African takeover regulations, Adapt IT has now appointed Nodus Capital TS as the independent expert to “express an opinion on whether the Huge offer consideration is fair and reasonable to Adapt IT shareholders, taking into account the value of Adapt IT’s shares”. Once received, the independent board will consider Nodus Capital’s opinion and will then “form its own opinion as to whether or not the Huge offer is fair and reasonable”, before advising shareholders.  — © 2021 NewsCentral Media This article was published with the permission of TechCentral, the original publication can be viewed here.